WEBVTT

00:00.073 --> 00:01.865
Thailand is a favorite country for tourists.

00:02.443 --> 00:04.597
There are numerous places to visit in Thailand.

00:05.060 --> 00:08.211
Whether you want national parks, jungles, cities or islands,...

00:08.479 --> 00:09.882
...there's a place in Thailand for you.

00:10.909 --> 00:12.875
With a tourist trail going back decades,...

00:13.184 --> 00:15.935
...Thailand is the heart of backpacking in Southeast Asia...

00:16.535 --> 00:21.066
...and you can get by on between 25 to 30 dollars a day, thanks to cheap guesthouses,...

00:21.883 --> 00:24.412
...food, local buses and attractions.

00:25.743 --> 00:29.487
If you spend all your time on the islands and inexpensive accommodation,...

00:29.659 --> 00:31.705
...expect to pay closer to 50 dollars a day.

